{"word":"σκυτοδέψης","slug":"σκυτοδέψης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σκυτοδέψης</b></el> <el>(σκῡτο-δέψης, ου, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δέφω'><el>δέφω</el></a>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <a href='S:δέψω'><el>δέψω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a leather-dresser, currier</i>, <b><a href='S:Theophrastus'>Theophr.</a></b>: so, <el>σκῡτόδεψος, ὁ</el>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/>"}]}